Depends: libc6 (>= 2.34), libjson-c5 (>= 0.15), librdkafka1 (>= 0.9.4), libssl3 (>= 3.0.0~~alpha1), zlib1g (>= 1:1.1.4), gunicorn, python3, python3-flask, python3-yaml, python3-simplejson, python3-flask-httpauth, python3-matplotlib, python3-cryptography, python3-qrcode, libavro23, python3-pil, zlib1g-dev, nagios-plugins, ksh, sysstat, libsys-statistics-linux-perl
Section: net
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://www.almondmonitor.com
Description: Local monitoring system running Nagios plugins and exposing the results through various means (http, api, metrics, kafka data stream)
 Full-featured local monitor that:
  - Runs Nagios plugins on a schedule
  - Exposes results via http, API and metrics endpoints
  - Streams data to Kafka for downstream consumers
